These are Puzzles for 7x3 Level 4

.:: Puzzle 7x3-Level-4-1::.
There are 3 different favourite beverages: fanta, hot-chocolate, soy-milk
There 3 different types of food: eggplant, nectarine, plum
The people have 3 different jobs:  dancer, manager, software-developer
The people have 3 different hobbies: traveling, video-games, reading
3 different games are played: whist, monopoly, go
There are 3 different nationalities: japanese, mexican, russian
City: new-york, marseilles, san-francisco
 1. the person playing whist is the person eating nectarine##1
 2. the manager is on the left or right of the russian##3
 3. the person who's hobby is video-games is on the left or right of the person traveling to san-francisco##3
 4. the dancer is the russian##1
 5. the person traveling to new-york is between the person eating plum and the person drinking soy-milk##2
 6. the person drinking hot-chocolate is in an odd position##4
 7. the person eating plum is on the left or right of the mexican##3
 8. the person who's hobby is reading is on the far right##1
 9. the person eating nectarine is between the japanese and the person playing monopoly##2
10. the person who's hobby is video-games is the manager##1
11. the person traveling to new-york is between the person who's hobby is reading and the russian##2
12. the person traveling to new-york is on the right of the person traveling to marseilles##1
13. the person traveling to san-francisco is the person drinking hot-chocolate##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1     |     2     |         3          |
| Beverage      | soy-milk | fanta     | hot-chocolate      |
| Food          | eggplant | nectarine | plum               |
| Job           | dancer   | manager   | software-developer |
| Hobby   | traveling  | video-games | reading           |
| Game   | monopoly  | whist   | go               |
| Nationality   | russian  | mexican   | japanese           |
| City           | marseilles   | new-york      | san-francisco              |

