.:: Puzzle 7x3-Level-4-2::.
There are 3 different favourite colors: chestnut, light-blue, orange
The people have 3 different hobbies: card-games, chess, traveling
The people's birthday is in 3 different months: april, october, february
The people prefer 3 different music-genres: disco, folk, hip-hop
There are 3 different favourite beverages: soy-milk, hot-chocolate, coffee
3 different pets are kept: frog, horse, turtle
The people prefer 3 different types of sport: baseball, parkour, swimming
 1. the person who's birthday is in october is on the left or right of the person who's hobby is traveling##3
 2. the owner of the frog is on the left or right of the owner of the turtle##3
 3. the owner of the turtle is in an odd position##4
 4. the person who's birthday is in april is the owner of the turtle##1
 5. the person who's sport is swimming is the person drinking hot-chocolate##1
 6. the person drinking soy-milk is on the left of the person who likes orange##1
 7. the person who's sport is baseball is the person who likes chestnut##1
 8. the fan of hip-hop is in the middle##1
 9. the person who likes chestnut is on the right of the fan of folk##1
10. the person drinking hot-chocolate is the person who's birthday is in april##1
11. the person who's hobby is chess is the person drinking coffee##1
12. the person who's birthday is in april is on the left or right of the person who's birthday is in february##3
13. the person who's sport is swimming is on the far right##1
14. the person drinking hot-chocolate is in an odd position##4
15. the owner of the frog is the owner of the frog##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1     |     2      |     3      |
| Color          | light-blue     | chestnut      | orange      |
| Hobby         | chess    | traveling  | card-games |
| Birthday           | october | february   | april |
| Music-Genre   | folk     | hip-hop    | disco      |
| Beverage   | coffee  | soy-milk | hot-chocolate    |
| Pet           | horse    | frog       | turtle     |
| Sport         | parkour  | baseball   | swimming   |

