.:: Puzzle 7x3-Level-4-3::.
There are 3 different favourite beverages: fanta, juice, lemonade
There 3 different types of food: cabbage, peach, watermelon
The people have 3 different jobs:  engineer, paramedic, project-manager
There are 3 different favourite colors: light-blue, brown, aquamarine
The people's birthday is in 3 different months: november, august, september
3 different pets are kept: cat, frog, snake
City: boston, berlin, liverpool
 1. the person who likes light-blue is on the far left or far right##3
 2. the person drinking juice is in an even position##4
 3. the person who's birthday is in september is on the far right##1
 4. the person eating watermelon is the person traveling to liverpool##1
 5. the person who likes aquamarine is on the far right##1
 6. the person who likes brown is between the person who's birthday is in november and the project-manager##2
 7. the person eating cabbage is on the left of the person traveling to liverpool##1
 8. the person eating watermelon is on the left or right of the person who's birthday is in august##3
 9. the owner of the frog is on the far left##1
10. the person drinking lemonade is the owner of the cat##1
11. the engineer is on the left of the paramedic##1
12. the person traveling to boston is on the far left##1
13. the person traveling to berlin is on the left or right of the person traveling to boston##3

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1     |     2     |        3        |
| Beverage      | fanta    | juice     | lemonade        |
| Food          | peach    | cabbage   | watermelon      |
| Job           | engineer | paramedic | project-manager |
| Color   | light-blue  | brown      | aquamarine           |
| Birthday   | november   | august | september        |
| Pet           | frog     | snake     | cat             |
| City     | boston     | berlin      | liverpool             |

