.:: Puzzle 7x3-Level-4-4::.
The people's birthday is in 3 different months: march, july, june
3 different brands of cigars are smoked: alhambra, ritmeester, bluemaster
The people have 3 different jobs:  mechanic, paramedic, scientist
The people perfer 3 different movie-genres: comedy, documentary, musical
City: edinburgh, nizza, rome
The people prefer 3 different types of sport: basketball, rugby, sailing
The people use 3 different means of transport: airplane, scooter, train
 1. the scientist is the alhambra-smoker##1
 2. the person driving the airplane is on the far right##1
 3. the person who's sport is sailing is the alhambra-smoker##1
 4. the mechanic is on the right of the person watching comedy movies##1
 5. the person watching documentary movies is on the right of the person who's birthday is in june##1
 6. the mechanic is the person who's sport is rugby##1
 7. the alhambra-smoker is the person driving the scooter##1
 8. the person traveling to rome is the person watching comedy movies##1
 9. the ritmeester-smoker is in an even position##4
10. the alhambra-smoker is the person who's birthday is in july##1
11. the person driving the scooter is the person traveling to nizza##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |     2      |      3      |
| Birthday      | july   | june      | march      |
| Cigar          | alhambra | ritmeester      | bluemaster      |
| Job           | scientist  | paramedic  | mechanic    |
| Movie-Genre   | musical    | comedy     | documentary |
| City   | nizza  | rome      | edinburgh     |
| Sport         | sailing    | basketball | rugby       |
| Transport     | scooter    | train      | airplane    |

