.:: Puzzle 7x3-Level-4-5::.
House: cottage, palace, tower
The people have 3 different jobs:  dressmaker, pilot, project-manager
City: san-francisco, boston, venice
The people grow 3 different varities of flowers: daisy, zinnia, tulip
There are 3 different nationalities: american, german, indonesian
The people prefer 3 different types of sport: basketball, soccer, water-polo
The people use 3 different means of transport: bus, scooter, tram
 1. the tower house is on the far right##1
 2. the person traveling to venice is on the right of the pilot##1
 3. the person traveling to venice is on the left of the person who growszinnia##1
 4. the person who growstulip is on the left or right of the palace house##3
 5. the person who's sport is basketball is on the left or right of the person who's sport is soccer##3
 6. the person who growszinnia is on the far left or far right##3
 7. the project-manager is the person traveling to venice##1
 8. the person traveling to san-francisco is the person driving the bus##1
 9. the person driving the tram is in an even position##4
10. the palace house is on the left or right of the person who growstulip##3
11. the indonesian is on the right of the person traveling to boston##1
12. the person who's sport is soccer is the pilot##1
13. the german is the person who growsdaisy##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |        2        |     3      |
| House         | palace | cottage           | tower    |
| Job           | pilot     | project-manager | dressmaker |
| City   | boston  | venice             | san-francisco  |
| Flower   | daisy     | tulip           | zinnia  |
| Nationality   | german    | indonesian      | american   |
| Sport         | soccer    | basketball      | water-polo |
| Transport     | scooter   | tram            | bus        |

