.:: Puzzle 7x3-Level-4-6::.
The people's birthday is in 3 different months: december, november, october
The people use 3 different means of transport: trike, quad-bike, airplane
The people have 3 different jobs:  scientist, security-guard, social-worker
The people prefer 3 different music-genres: blues, country, pop
There are 3 different nationalities: chinese, egyptian, mexican
3 different pets are kept: dog, frog, hedgehog
3 different brands of cigars are smoked: ritmeester, swisher, davidoff
 1. the owner of the hedgehog is on the left or right of the davidoff-smoker##3
 2. the fan of pop is on the left or right of the scientist##3
 3. the fan of country is between the swisher-smoker and the person driving the quad-bike##2
 4. the person who's birthday is in october is the owner of the frog##1
 5. the chinese is on the far left##1
 6. the person driving the quad-bike is on the right of the scientist##1
 7. the owner of the hedgehog is on the right of the davidoff-smoker##1
 8. the fan of blues is on the left or right of the egyptian##3
 9. the security-guard is on the left of the person who's birthday is in december##1
10. the person driving the trike is in an even position##4
11. the person who's birthday is in december is on the left of the fan of blues##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |       1        |     2     |       3       |
| Birthday      | october         | december  | november      |
| Transport         | airplane        | trike   | quad-bike    |
| Job           | security-guard | scientist | social-worker |
| Music-Genre   | pop            | country   | blues         |
| Nationality   | chinese        | egyptian  | mexican       |
| Pet           | frog           | dog       | hedgehog      |
| Cigar         | swisher           | davidoff   | ritmeester       |

