There are 3 different favourite colors: light-blue, pink, turquise
 1. the fan of punk is the owner of the guinea-pig##1
 2. the person watching animation movies is on the right of the person who likes light-blue##1
 3. the german is on the right of the owner of the frog##1
 4. the fan of gospel is the person watching disaster movies##1
 5. the owner of the frog is the fan of soul##1
 6. the person drinking mirinda is on the far right##1
 7. the german is on the left or right of the person eating nectarine##3
 8. the owner of the dog is on the far left or far right##3
 9. the french is between the person eating pineapple and the fan of gospel##2
10. the german is on the far left or far right##3
11. the person who likes pink is the person who likes pink##1
12. the owner of the guinea-pig is in an odd position##4
13. the person drinking milk is the person who likes pink##1
14. the person watching animation movies is on the far left or far right##3
15. the person eating nectarine is on the left or right of the person eating cauliflower##3

