 7. the fan of trance is on the left or right of the owner of the cat##3
 8. the modern house is the person eating pineapple##1
 9. the person who growsbegonia is on the right of the modern house##1
10. the person who's sport is parkour is the person drinking juice##1
11. the owner of the guinea-pig is on the right of the art-deco house##1

